{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>不過其中一本雜誌封面似乎有人體寫真的藝術作品，風格十分大膽前衛，引來不少內地網友怒批「很土」、「擦邊女」，更指她愛裝小眾，而她似乎忍無可忍，直接在幾名嗆聲網友留言下用官方帳號回嗆，強硬態度立刻登上熱搜榜。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125431901759213568574861.jpeg/FA1OQWz4Hkc4_7LrNVfkVPNa1mEeEPgYKtBTUSrQU1E\" alt=\"aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）\"><figcaption>aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）</figcaption></figure><p>更多aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓的相片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125434088644153344741862.jpeg/q1wyUchsyivfuTN4SGQ68fREakbSIkUhTuCDdk7gg3Y\" alt=\"aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓所發的雜誌封面（Instagram@imnotningning）\"><figcaption>aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓所發的雜誌封面（Instagram@imnotningning）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125434090938568704597318.jpeg/lWTw9P4XaZ_WZ9M91MZaQLH8IS5cdIyoTpRGXk6URl4\" alt=\"aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓被網民狂轟的相片（Instagram@imnotningning）\"><figcaption>aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓被網民狂轟的相片（Instagram@imnotningning）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125433700138356736521960.jpeg/py4l891aimWiyrEvxx_dIhQUjt8tqjtFijIi4YoyIuE\" alt=\"aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）\"><figcaption>aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125433702327914496628057.jpeg/JgVktjutkdlzlJglYdQXPW4BRAY1Vx7ZjKCCHoyggh4\" alt=\"aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）\"><figcaption>aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125433704722993152975082.jpeg/gU-gkz_s-H2m-nBLfAcVZMfP8E110995VtbI61bWyOs\" alt=\"aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）\"><figcaption>aespa中國籍成員Ningning寧藝卓（Instagram@imnotningning）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125433707126460416037594.jpeg/wJfilZepNlLJ